807
00:44:18,046 --> 00:44:20,396
Let me get you out
of your jacket. Come on.

808
00:45:07,182 --> 00:45:09,532
- I bet you it's even more
beautiful in the summer.

809
00:45:09,619 --> 00:45:11,230
- Oh, it sure is.

810
00:45:11,317 --> 00:45:14,842
