00:48:30,777 --> 00:48:33,040
- Yes. I'm super happy.

859
00:48:33,127 --> 00:48:34,520
I'm glad you brought
some holiday spirit

860
00:48:34,607 --> 00:48:36,348
back into this lonely house.

861
00:48:36,435 --> 00:48:39,046
Thank you.

862
00:48:39,133 --> 00:48:40,569
- Of course.

