00:59:34,962 --> 00:59:36,355
- Thank you, Dominik.

997
00:59:49,020 --> 00:59:52,501
Thank you, Vienna.
Not gonna cost a thing.

998
00:59:52,589 --> 00:59:54,503
- Thank you for making me
go to the doctor.

